title: Star players on the move
itunes:title: Star players on the move
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal – discuss all the latest news from around the NFL, including Panthers defensive end Jared Allen announcing his retirement, and the latest on the Kirk Cousins contract negotiations with the redskins. Then, the heroes go in-depth into the 2016 free agent class, including which players are on the bubble of being cut this offseason. Then finally, the heroes dip into the old ATN mailbag to answer a few listener questions.
